CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B6, reads: "HAPPY - Mrs. Jean Nelson Harvey, wife of the Rev. William J. Harvey III, of Pittsburgh, and Mrs. Helena Sims, of Baton Rouge, La., happily pose before receiving their Master of Education Degrees"
TitMainTitle: Jean Nelson Harvey and Helena Sims wearing dark caps and gowns, and light colored stoles, after receiving Master of Education Degrees, at University of Pittsburgh graduation
